Description:
City Pop - Your flexible solution for long and short stays, making you feel at home.
Starting from 490 CHF/week up to 650 CHF/week, we offer centrally located apartments in Zurich, ranging from approximately 24-54 square meters. We provide various types of apartments: Pop S Compact, S M, XL, or 2.5 locals. These furnished apartments ensure an authentic living experience where you can relax, work, sleep, cook, and dine, all in a space that resembles the interior of a 4-star hotel:
Fully furnished apartments with a kitchen, living room, sleeping area, and bathroom;
Complete kitchen inventory (cutlery, glasses, plates, etc.);
Bedding and bathroom towels provided;
Utilities included (electricity, water);
Fast Wi-Fi connection;
Smart TV;
Complimentary breakfast (croissant and coffee).
But that's not all! This fantastic and innovative living concept has no contractual restrictions on the minimum length of stay: City Pop can be booked for 4 weeks up to a maximum of 52 weeks. A wide range of standard and additional services is available, which can be easily activated through our City-Pop-App:
Cleaning service (weekly, biweekly);
Storage box;
Laudry;
Moreover, the building is equipped with cool shared spaces (at affordable prices)
Gym;
Co-working;
Terrace;
Bike parking
Each guest can tailor and customize their own package of services to best suit their needs and lifestyle. Booking an apartment is as simple as reserving a hotel room! To book an apartment and check availability, download our City Pop App, select your desired booking period, and you'll have access to all available apartments during that time. For more information, visit our website or use our App called City Pop!
We are excited to welcome you at City Pop!

